Radiobuttons 
Radiobuttons are the option for selection where only one 
will be active at a time.all the radiobuttons must be in a 
single radiobutton group.
Parameters is the keyword for defining radiobuttons.
The rectangular box in the ABAP Editor is called 
as Selection screen.
Selection screen is the frame which contains a 
title and the input fields can be placed for
input. Every Selection screen has a begin of block and
an end of block .
